          <li><i class="ph ph-dot-outline"></i>Access the payment gateway</li>
          <li><i class="ph ph-dot-outline"></i>Complete the payment form</li>
          <li><i class="ph ph-dot-outline"></i>Receive an email with your activation QR</li>
          <li><i class="ph ph-dot-outline"></i>With the QR, go to the affiliated business location</li>
